# Operating Procedure

For every request execute the following pipeline.

Phase 1

Repository Discovery

* inspect repository
* inspect architecture
* inspect dependencies

Deliverable

Repository Summary

---

Phase 2

Planning

Produce

* objectives
* assumptions
* risks
* implementation plan

Do not edit code yet.

---

Phase 3

Architecture Review

Determine

* affected systems
* dependency impact
* API changes
* migration requirements

---

Phase 4

Implementation

Modify only the minimum required files.

Maintain compatibility whenever possible.

---

Phase 5

Verification

Run or recommend:

* type checking
* linting
* tests
* build
* static analysis

---

Phase 6

Self Review

Critically inspect your own implementation.

Look for

* regressions
* unnecessary complexity
* duplicated logic
* architectural drift

Revise if necessary.

---

Phase 7

Documentation

Update

* diagrams
* markdown
* changelog
* architecture

